values: My journal is now mostly friends only. Please leave a comment if you would like to follow along.

Are you a fan of Battlestar Galactica? I'm looking to recruite more members in the Houston, TX area for  Colonial Defense forces.  The idea is to start a chapter of the fan club here locally once there is enough interest. For more information read on: Colonial Defense Forces

Thought it was time to change the look of my journal.

Which reminds me where is a good female villan when you need one.

Ok so maybe I'm still in that same reflective mood that started way too early this morning when I 
had trouble sleeping. So enough on that its time for me to see if tonight is any better.
